source.name: Public Company Bankruptcy Cases Opened and Monitored for Fiscal Year 2009
source.description: This file contains all of the bankruptcy cases for public companies opened and monitored in the fiscal year 2009. The data includes the District Court, the state, the company name, assets, and liabilities.
